name: Las Terrazas
highlight: "“A modern and spacious villa ideally located close to the sparkling waters of Cala Bassa"”

children.text:
This lovely 6 bedroom villa is conveniently situated next to the crystal clear waters of Cala Bassa, one of the most beloved beaches on the island, and only a short drive from Cala Tarida and Cala Conte's famed sunset beaches. The picturesque village of San Jose is within easy reach and celebrates a lively cafe culture, as is the capital of the island Ibiza Town with its many dancing and dining destinations.
The interiors are elegant and stylish throughout, each room offers large windows and sliding glass doors. The interior design is what really makes this home special, you can quickly discover beautiful, trendy furniture, decorations and ornaments in each and every room, creating a sophisticated sense of designer living. The friendly lounge area provides the perfect space to soak up the atmosphere, and a professionally fitted kitchen supports a large interior dining area.

With its own distinctive style, each bedroom is stylishly completed, and the spacious layout ensures that visitors appreciate a true sense of space and privacy. The added bonus of underfloor heating makes this beautiful home ideal for living all year round.

The outdoor spaces provide a relaxing atmosphere where visitors can admire the lush gardens, from the magnificent pine forest behind the house to the abundance of fragrant floral plantations and fruit trees. An elegant terrace, complete with ample sun loungers and shaded cabanas, is surrounded by a welcoming saltwater pool. The dedicated alfresco dining area is the perfect spot to spend long lazy lunches with friends and family or starlit evenings, while you totally immerse yourself in the natural beauty of your setting with a drink in hand.
